Pamela, 55, revisited her iconic look in a red hot dress at the LA premiere of her tell-all Netflix documentary. Pamela put her best fashion foot forward at the Los Angeles premiere of her tell-all Netflix documentary, Pamela: A Love Story, on Monday. The Baywatch star showed off her toned physique and sculpted arms in a red hot floor-length gown that clung to her figure. The actress was also joined by her sons Brandon Thomas, 26, and Dylan Lee, 25, whom she shares with ex-husband Tommy Lee, 60. Pamela paired the red hot look with matching stilettos as she turned heads on the red carpet.